      "created_at": "2018-04-08T15:55:13.173Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Gezuar Pashket. Pamje nga Manastriri i Ardenices.<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/102edb919d782217940ab843156b8d1df080936f.jpg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"696\" height=\"418\"></p>",
