    {
      "id": 72014,
      "post_number": 15,
      "username": "Alba2265",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/85e7bf/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-08T16:29:22.804Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Eshte metafore .pavaresisht nga trials e tribulations of today e mira do te triumfoje .interesant eshte fakti se lufterat uria semundjet ne bibel referohen si dhimbjet e lindjes metafore qe diku e perdor edhe engelsi pothuaj 2000 vjet me pas duke e pershkruar violencen  si dhimbjet e lindjes te nje shoqerie te re.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 3,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 72015,
      "post_number": 16,
      "username": "TironciLebetit",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/tironcilebetit/{size}/64_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-08T16:37:17.396Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Te them te drejten Manastiri i Ardenices eshte njesoj  sic e kam lene ne 1991.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/63ba5f623a1f45c8cbcf446926428c543ed0f892.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/63ba5f623a1f45c8cbcf446926428c543ed0f892\" title=\"image.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/63ba5f623a1f45c8cbcf446926428c543ed0f892.jpg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/63ba5f623a1f45c8cbcf446926428c543ed0f892_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">900×600 239 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Duhet te jete vene dore tek kjo kulla e bardhe.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9a2b185ea1c3c8af626515819fe573523b6c2829.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/9a2b185ea1c3c8af626515819fe573523b6c2829\" title=\"image.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9a2b185ea1c3c8af626515819fe573523b6c2829.jpg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9a2b185ea1c3c8af626515819fe573523b6c2829_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">900×600 142 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Nashti Qisha e Re e stermadhe Lexhendare, mu ne mes te Tiranes, qe ka ndertuar Janulla me duket si fallco e shume Greke. Me vjen keq qe Qisha e mbijetuar Komunizmes perballe ish Muzeut te Natyres, ngjitur me fushat e qymyrit, eshte braktisur dhe gjithe vemendjen e ka marre kjo Gerdalla e re me ngjyra shkelqyese e Janulles.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 14,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 72019,
      "post_number": 17,
      "username": "korriku",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/korriku/{size}/18544_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-08T17:01:40.541Z",
      "cooked": "<p>duhet te jete ndertuar thjesht per te zene truallin ne pronesi, nje injorance ndertimi mu ne bash te vendit. Kushedi a zhbehen dot budallalleqe bombastike si ajo kishe ne kryeqytet.<br>\nQendrat me te vogla administrative duhet te jene plot me simotra te kesaj .</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox whitelistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9eeb2b0529d3c8065e4edb06fb75bb7cf9a6e5a1.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"65\" height=\"65\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.kultplus.com/foto-lajm/pamje-e-mrekullueshme-e-lindjes-se-diellit-ne-manastirin-e-ardenices/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"11:20AM - 27 August 2017\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">KultPlus – 27 Aug 17</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:800/533;\"><img src=\"https://www.kultplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/21056044_10155084005416523_4979561076085360017_o-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.kultplus.com/foto-lajm/pamje-e-mrekullueshme-e-lindjes-se-diellit-ne-manastirin-e-ardenices/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Pamje e mrekullueshme e lindjes së diellit në Manastirin e Ardenicës</a></h3>\n\n<p>Manastiri i Ardenicës gjendet në jugperëndim të qytetit të Lushnjës në Shqipëri buzë rrugës kombëtare që lidh qytetin e Fierit me atë të Lushnjës në një pozitë dominuese në kodrat me të njëjtin emër, në lartësinë 237m mbi nivelin e detit. Manastiri...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
      "reply_to_post_number": 16,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 72022,
      "post_number": 18,
      "username": "Alba2265",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/85e7bf/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-08T17:14:50.563Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ka bere dicka te pakten .erioni na dha haberin e gezuar se do ndertonet edhe qisha e shen prokopit ,xhamia me e madhe ne Balkan po ashtu .po harrin suksese shume te medhaja populli yne <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/blush.png?v=5\" title=\":blush:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":blush:\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 16,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 72024,
      "post_number": 19,
      "username": "TironciLebetit",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/tironcilebetit/{size}/64_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-08T17:17:06.409Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Kena ene byrazerat e Erdoganit qe do ndertojne nje super xhami mu ne bash te vendit me 4 minare.<br>\n<a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/alba2265\">@Alba2265</a> Janullatosi ka bere shume ne fakt ne qytetet e Shqiperise per sa i perket qishave lokale, ket ne tirone e ka bo Quditshem dhe me elemente Janullatos Narcisist.<br>\nJanulla per mua tek kisha e Shen Prokopit fuhet ti kish hudh lekat por se bon se eshte qishe me te kaluar shqiptare e pa elemente Grek por Vlleh.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 17,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 72025,
      "post_number": 20,
      "username": "Alba2265",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/85e7bf/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-08T17:23:17.157Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ndonje haber se u ngrit nje community college psh qe pregatit technicians per industrial maintenance,robotics ,cnc etj sikur nuk po vjen nga vatani .</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 19,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
